{"tid":557253,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"如何取代Adobe","createTime":"2018-02-11T07:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T04:35:23.000Z","uid":136686,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b4ff604ce7db1e1eb6165e745d12bc79b1d6f6ca","tid":557253,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T07:32:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n用太多開心版擔心版權問題<br />\n<del>那個偽官方免費CS2版本已經無法滿足需求</del><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我打算一個人在家中做動畫<del>或者互動遊戲</del><br />\n打算買一個Live2D Cubism3回來做動畫<br />\n<del>免費試用版太多限制,所以這筆錢省不下</del><br />\n<br />\nLive2D Cubism3的基本操作都會<br />\n但單靠Live2D並不能做到甚麼<br />\n<br />\n繪師畫給我的圖需要用Photoshop處理(除非她已經把圖層處理妥當)<br />\nLive2D輪出的素材動畫,需要透過Premiere 和 After Effect 這對姊妹做後期處理和剪接<br />\n<br />\n<del>如果要做互動程式,需要輸出往Unity<br />\n然後學一堆C#才能控制妥當</del><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果在使用正版軟件的前題下<br />\nLive2D一個月$140左右<br />\n整套Adobe一個月$500 (一個軟件250,一套500)<br />\n<br />\n要記住,這不是買斷制,是按月收費...<br />\nLive2D是必須品,但Adobe這一筆真的有點貴<br />\n<br />\n除了破解以外有甚麼辦法可以省下Adobe這一筆月費<br />\n例如是能取代 Photoshop , Premiere 和 After Effect 的免費/買斷制軟件"},{"pid":"b2eab543502afb134541256d50cf486660be7104","tid":557253,"uid":108502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"小畫家?"},{"pid":"1cb92f8b69654cd9f3b0cf95c5ed7117232cda99","tid":557253,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"認真答你<br />\nKrita"},{"pid":"e1fa1fa2dcd53b5ef92f6dfa545ee2874a831281","tid":557253,"uid":108502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cb92f8b69654cd9f3b0cf95c5ed7117232cda99","tid":557253,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"認真答你<br />\nKrita"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T07:47:21.000Z","msg":"介面同Ps差唔多<br />\n又可以開到PS啲file<br />\n又免費<br />\nWindows Linux Mac都有"},{"pid":"327c323f519b122884f4a2b589204682eb61affb","tid":557253,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b2eab543502afb134541256d50cf486660b